snippet.title: VE-S2R4P: Antibody Mediated Prevention Trial: Where to from here?
snippet.description:
This presentation recorded during HIVR4P // Virtual is part of the DESIGN APPROACHES FOR CURRENT AND FUTURE HIV PREVENTION EFFICACY TRIALS - VIRTUAL WORKSHOP SERIES (OCTOBER 2020 TO MAY 2021) organized by the Global HIV Vaccine Enterprise in partnership with the HIV Vaccine and Prevention Trials Networks and the Forum for Collaborative Research.

Link: https://vaccineenterprise.org/hiv-prevention-clinical-trial-design-of-the-future

Music: Scott Holmes (scottholmesmusic.com).
